<pb n="0905c" xml:id="T21.1385.0905c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0905c01" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>達哩摩<note place="inline">二合引</note>𧹞<note place="inline">引十三</note>誐拏鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>嚩囉<note place="inline">十四</note>
<lb n="0905c02" ed="T"/>商伽薩爹嚩<note place="inline">引</note>計曳<note place="inline">二合引</note>那<note place="inline">十五</note>遏儞<note place="inline">引</note>那薩爹
